{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.15.1503;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs20 The full changelog of TortoiseSVN:\par
\f1\par
Version 1.0.3\par
- ADD: It's now possible to invoke the add command on\par
       already versioned folders to add unversioned \par
       files inside that folder. (Stefan)\par
- CHG: The URL entry field now looks and behaves much more\par
       like the one in Internet Explorer (Thomas)\par
- CHG: TortoiseMerge now works on NT4 as well. (Thomas Girard)\par
- BUG: The overlay icons did not work on some machines\par
       correctly or not at all. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: committing a renamed directory didn't work. (Stefan)\par
\f0\par
\f1 Version 1.0.2\par
- ADD: Find dialog for TortoiseMerge. (Stefan)\par
- CHG: Improved checking for correctness of revision\par
       number fields (Thomas Epting)\par
- CHG: When "Ignore all whitespaces" is active and \par
       "don't show whitespaces" then the line diff bar\par
       doesn't show those whitespaces. (Stefan)\par
- CHG: The context menus can now be activated by\par
       either a right-click or the special\par
       windows key or shift-F10. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: Remove compiler optimizations which lead \par
       to a crash in the repo browser. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: Applying a patch which had the whole file\par
       deleted lead to a crash. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: TortoiseMerge showed error when the mousepointer\par
       moved past the last line in one-pane view. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: When sorting the files/folders in the commit dialog\par
       the "(P only)" mark got lost. (Stefan)\par
\par
Version 1.0.1\par
- ADD: The dialog asking the user to enter an URL (e.g.\par
       for the repo browser) has now a history of\par
       the last used URL's for the user to select from. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: New option to use a short version of the date\par
       for log messages. (Thomas Epting)\par
- ADD: The property page now shows the subversion\par
       properties in a combobox. \par
       There's also a tooltip showing additional\par
       information about the svn: properties. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: Ability to use different merge/diff programs\par
       for different filetypes. (Thomas Epting)\par
- ADD: Warn the user before creating a repository\par
       on a network share. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: Warn the user if (s)he tries to checkout/import\par
       via file to a repository on a network share. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: TortoiseMerge shows the line numbers \par
       in the views. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: Autopatch function to patch all files \par
       automatically. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: Line diff bar at the bottom of the two pane\par
       view, showing the two lines above each other\par
       (if the lines are different). Issue 88. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: A magnifier for the locatorbar in TME. (Stefan)\par
- CHG: Many cosmetic changes to the UI. (Stefan)\par
- CHG: The log dialog shows now the log messages\par
       in the fourth column (a short version) so\par
       you can see the logs without clicking on\par
       the revision. (Thomas Epting)\par
- CHG: The font combobox now only shows each font\par
       once. (Stefan)\par
- CHG: Updated TortoisePlink to 0.53b - now \par
       includes proxy support. \par
- BUG: If the "Check for updates" dialog is started\par
       for a file (not for a folder), the filename\par
       wasn't shown. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: Fix various bugs with svn:externals and the\par
       commit/add dialogs. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: The shell part didn't have the APR_ICONV_PATH\par
       environement variable set. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: Various bugfixes for TortoiseMerge. (Stefan)\par
\par
Version 1.0\par
- ADD: New option in the settings dialog to set the \par
       filetimes to the last commit time. This solves\par
       issue 83. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: From the log dialog it's now possible to start\par
       the repository browser so it browses the\par
       selected revision. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: New button in the settings dialog to open\par
       the subversion config file with the default\par
       text editor. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: Implement Issue 87. TortoiseMerge shows now\par
       the filename and the revision in the viewtitle.\par
       TME gets this information from TSVN. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: The repository browser now allows the selection\par
       of more than one item. With this, the user can\par
       now select two files/folders from different\par
       urls (e.g. trunk and tags) and request a diff\par
       from them. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: Implement a "Delete" command in the context menu of \par
       the commit dialog for unversioned files. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: TortoiseMerge can now handle UTF8 files. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: Selecting of lines and copying them to the\par
       clipboard in TortoiseMerge. (Stefan)\par
- CHG: Use of an iterator to gather all the files\par
       needed for import/commit/add. This saves a lot\par
       of memory and is also a big speedup for large\par
       directories. (Jon Foster)\par
- CHG: The log message editboxes now do "soft-wrap",\par
       i.e. the logmessage is wrapped at the right\par
       end of the dialog box. (Stefan)\par
- CHG: "Show unversioned files before committing" is now\par
       enabled by default. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: In TME it was not possible to select a diff block\par
       completely if it started at the first line. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: Creating a branch/tag from a modified working\par
       copy did not include the changes from the\par
       working copy! (Stefan)\par
- BUG: In the Commit and the Add dialog: if a file was\par
       selected then only the topmost parentfolder was\par
       automatically selected instead of all intermediant\par
       parentfolders. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: Export always used HEAD, even if another revision\par
       was specified in the dialog. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: Showing diffs for changed files from the list in\par
       the log dialog was done with the wrong revisions. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: When adding files in a directory with svn:externals\par
       in it already controlled files got shown in\par
       the add dialog. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: Some patchfiles were not parsed correctly. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: Fixed a massive memory leak when showing logs,\par
       also reduced memory consumption when \par
       committing. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: If the config file was messed up with TSVN just\par
       crashed instead of showing the error and exit. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: When sorting by a column in the commit dialog\par
       the selections (checkboxes) got lost. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: When the recursive overlay was activated, the\par
       overlays for folders weren't shown recursive if\par
       the explorer columns weren't sorted by name. (Stefan)\par
\f0\par
\f1 Version 0.26\par
- ADD: The columns in the progress and the commit dialog \par
       are now sortable. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: It's possible now to drag on the locatorbar\par
       in TME. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: TME now shows ToolTips for the filenames in\par
       each view to make it easier to see the\par
       full path. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: New context menu to open files with the\par
       default application in the commit dialog. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: By placing a '#' in front of the paths for the\par
       external diff/merge programs make TSVN use\par
       it's own program TortoiseMerge. This helps\par
       users who want to switch easily between\par
       two different programs. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: german translation of the TSVN docs. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: the helpfile is chosen according to the\par
       selected language. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: Configurable font and fontsize in TME. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: Configurable font and fontsize for log messages\par
       in TSVN. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: Log messages could be shown with an additional\par
       empty line between the normal lines. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: The filepaths in the log messages were\par
       shown twice. (Stefan)       \par
- BUG: If a difference was only one line then\par
       TME skipped that when it should have gone\par
       there on file load. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: Filenames with ";" in it could not be\par
       committed. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: The groupbox text was shown black in the\par
       settings dialog on some systems. (Stefan)\par
\par
Version 0.25\par
- ADD: TME shows the differences in whitespaces\par
       inside a line too. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: New option to not convert files before\par
       diffing with BASE. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: By pressing F5 in the commit dialog you\par
       can refresh the file list. (Stefan)\par
- CHG: Enable the left view on loading files\par
       in TME. (Stefan)\par
- CHG: Use a fixed width font for log messages as\par
       default, selectable in the settings dialog. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: Fixed a bug in LogDlg, where Double-click \par
       and right-click behaved differently. \par
       Double-Click tried to fetch the log for \par
       a wrong revision. (Luebbe)\par
- BUG: Fixed a crash if the patchfile to apply contained\par
       a new but empty file. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: Don't try to show the context menu in TME for\par
       the view title. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: Bring the progress window to front even after\par
       a confirmation dialog. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: Pressing a key while the log dialog fetches\par
       all messages (or even after that) could\par
       throw an error. (Stefan)\par
       \f0\par
Version 0.24\par
- ADD: A new separate program to apply patches,\par
       showing diffs and resolving conflicts.\par
       The program is called TortoiseMerge.\par
       (Stefan)\par
- ADD: New command to create patchfiles in\par
       unified diff format from a modified\par
       working copy. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: New command to apply patchfiles in\par
       unified diff format to a working\par
       copy. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: New checkbox to select/deselect all entries\par
       in the commit dialog. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: A doubleclick on a file/entry in the log dialog\par
       starts the diff viewer. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: Doubleclicking on merged files in the update\par
       progress dialog starts the diff viewer. (Stefan)\par
- CHG: The settings dialog got a facelift. (Stefan)\par
- CHG: The layout in our installation folder\par
       is more organized. (Stefan)\par
- CHG: The about box got a facelift: it finally\par
       has the correct TSVN logo in it. (Stefan)\par
- CHG: Don't show an error if a temporary file\par
       can't get deleted because of a stupid\par
       virus scanner. (Stefan)\par
- CHG: The log dialog now shows the file/foldername\par
       for which the log is requested in the\par
       window title. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: Convert the Subversion error messages\par
       properly from UTF8 to UNICODE/MBCS. (Stefan)\par
\par
Version 0.23\par
- ADD: Most dialogs now have the "F1"-help\par
       working. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: The commit dialog now shows a busy cursor\par
       while the status of the working copy files\par
       is checked. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: The property page and the repo browser showed\par
       some garbage characters instead of clean\par
       Unicode chars. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: Folders with a "d" at the beginning could\par
       be shown wrong in the repository browser. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: In the property page the properties were\par
       not set to the selected value in the\par
       list-control. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: Fixed a registry handle leak in the shell\par
       extension. (Stefan)\par
       \par
Version 0.22\par
- ADD: A lot of improved icons. (Luebbe)\par
- ADD: Hint text for the setting "don't remove\par
       log messages when cancelling a commit". (Stefan)\par
- ADD: The "Add before commit" option allows now\par
       to add whole unversioned folders to be\par
       added before a commit. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: The commit dialog has a context menu from\par
       where its possible to revert changes\par
       in listed files. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: Doubleclicking on a locally modified entry\par
       in the "Check For Updates" dialog opens\par
       the diff-viewer. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: Reduce memory footprint of the status\par
       cache. (Stefan Fuhrmann)\par
- BUG: If the log dialog already showed all\par
       revisions the first time then disable\par
       the "Get All" button. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: TSVN could crash during authentication\par
       when fetching the remote status. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: After an update, the "Show Log..." \par
       only showed the last revision instead\par
       of all revisions since the last\par
       update. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: When looking for the associated program\par
       for a specific filetype (e.g. *.txt)\par
       the environement variables weren't\par
       expanded. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: TSVN could crash in the log dialog if\par
       the status of a file or folder could\par
       not be read. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: The status strings weren't localized\par
       in the commit and "Check for Updates"\par
       dialog. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: Menu settings could be ignored if \par
       the first settings change is to put\par
       all menu entries in the submenu. If\par
       any other setting was made first then\par
       everything was ok. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: When creating a folder on the repository\par
       root in the browser the refresh function\par
       went too far up. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: If no log entry was selected a right-click\par
       or a left-click on the message area below\par
       crashed the log dialog.\par
       The log dialog crashed if a key was pressed\par
       before any log messages got received. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: The repository browser handled the "+" sign\par
       in e.g svn+ssh:// url incorrectly.\par
       Also the "+" sign was missing in the\par
       explorer property page. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: svn+ssh didn't work at all until now. Thanks\par
       to Bjoern Kuenstig we were able to make\par
       it work. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: The dialog presented before an export had\par
       some labels/title mention "Checkout" instead\par
       of "Export" which confused some people. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: Deleting the temp files in the import dialog\par
       did not work if a file _and_ the parent\par
       folder were selected for deletion. (Stefan)\par
\par
       \par
Version 0.21\par
- ADD: If multiple targets are selected for\par
       update the all targets which belong to\par
       the same repository (have the same uuid)\par
       are updated to the same revision, no matter\par
       if another commit happened in between\par
       those updates. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: Subversion got a new command: "Blame".\par
       TSVN has it too :) What it does?\par
       It shows you for each line in a file\par
       the revision it was last changed and\par
       the author (so you can blame a bug\par
       on that author :). (Stefan)\par
- ADD: The show log command now only shows\par
       the last 100 revisions, configurable\par
       in the settings dialog. A new "Get All"\par
       button then fetches the rest of the log\par
       messages if needed. (Stefan)\par
- CHG: Rewrite of the status cache. The time\par
       for sorting a by a column should now\par
       take much less time and scale much\par
       better than before. (Stefan)\par
- CHG: Don't error out when doing a merge \par
       if the wc has been changed. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: Empty lines were not shown in log\par
       messages. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: Temp files weren't deleted before an\par
       import even if they were marked for\par
       deletion. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: The log message when creating a new\par
       folder was always the same. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: Changes made on folders in the repo-\par
       browser weren't shown (refresh did\par
       not work). (Stefan)\par
- BUG: "An invalid argument was encountered"\par
       in the log-dialog when working only\par
       with keyboard got fixed. (Stefan)\par
\par
Version 0.20.2\par
- BUG: crash bug not fixed in 0.20.1 (one Ctrl-Z\par
       to remove debugging code too much :)\par
       (Stefan)\par
       \par
Version 0.20.1\par
- BUG: A crash occured if the ssh settings were\par
       not empty. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: Main page in the settings dialog lost\par
       the language settings if the combo-box\par
       wasn't touched. (Stefan)\par
\par
Version 0.20\par
- BUG: The property page was always shown in english,\par
       no matter what language was set. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: The repository browser didn't work for file:///\par
       URLs which had escaped chars in it. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: If the "X"-Button of the progress window was\par
       pressed twice the window just hang. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: The external merge program was started\par
       with the filenames only instead of the\par
       full filepaths. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: The status cache wasn't thread-safe and\par
       also not process-safe. Thanks to Luebbe\par
