       (Stefan)\par
- CHG: The context menu is disabled for ".svn"\par
       directories. (Stefan)\par
- CHG: The balloon tooltips have now the standard\par
       color of windows as the background. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: Branch/Tag is available for single files\par
       too, not just folders. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: Several new commands for the repository\par
       browser. Also a new command in the context\par
       menu to start the repo browser. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: If a conflict occurs during an update/merge\par
       operation you can now just doubleclick on\par
       the conflicted entry to start the external\par
