       \par
Version 0.19\par
- BUG: The conflicted files weren't always determined\par
       correctly. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: The settings page for the menu layout set the\par
       settings to the default values if the page\par
       wasn't selected. (Dimentiy)\par
- BUG: File-entries in the log dialog could not be\par
       selected if the message contained more than\par
       three lines. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: Issue 67: Show Log + Escape = crash. fixed. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: There was a memory leak which made explorer use\par
       a huge amount of RAM over time. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: The cache timeout wasn't calculated correctly.\par
       This lead to wrong icon overlays and needed\par
       several "F5" to get the right ones. (Stefan)\par
- CHG: The "rename" command now uses the --force option\par
       by default so that modified files can be renamed\par
       too. (Stefan)\par
- CHG: The log dialog got minimize/maximize buttons. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: Log messages selectable to copy them to the\par
       clipboard (with Ctrl-C). Issue 64. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: Search function for log messages. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: Properties can be set/removed recursively. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: "Find" button in the merge dialog for finding\par
       the revision at which the branch occurred.\par
       Also the log dialog is shown to help decide\par
       which revisions should be merged in.\par
       Please note: this works only correct if the\par
       server has subversion 0.28 and higher! (Stefan)\par
- ADD: Commands "diff", "gnudiff" in the "Changed Files"\par
       dialog work now for wc-changes too.\par
       Also added a "revert" command. (Stefan)\par
- ADD: The "show log" button is activated not only\par
       after updates but also after switch (if the\par
       revision number after the switch is higher\par
       than before). (Stefan)\par
- ADD: The property page is now shown for multiple\par
       files too (without the information about\par
       a file, since every file has different\par
       status, dates, names, ...). This allows\par
       to set/remove properties on multiple files\par
       at once. (Stefan)\par
\par
