- BUG: The repository browser didn't escape the url\par
       sequences. (Stefan)\par
- BUG: Explorer could crash when doing a column sort\par
       on really big working copies. Thanks a lot\par
       to L\'fcbbe for helping in finding this bug. (Stefan)\par
