- BUG: the "Add" and "Add to ignore list" commands were\par
       shown even if there was no working copy. (Stefan)\par
- CHG: URL's are shown unescaped now, at least everywhere\par
       where they can't be edited. (Stefan)\par
- CHG: Follow the drive type settings: don't access\par
